description.narrative:
The project objectives are: 

* SO1: Empowering refugees and migrants in dealing with an unknown and distressing context with more autonomy; 
* SO2: Contributing to improving material living conditions of migrants and refugees in Istanbul; 
* SO3: Increasing awareness and coordinated action for refugees and migrants, on churches, NGOs and local groups’ level 
* SO4: Improving psychological condition of refugee and migrant women, reducing the stress and isolation they experience 
living in a foreign country
